{"tid":1575780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「撤銷控罪」重要過「獨立調查委員會」","createTime":"2019-09-17T03:21:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T03:31:16.000Z","uid":126621,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a59181691b35acd2386588109d1143ba64b61e35","tid":1575780,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:21:55.000Z","msg":"雖然我都唔想比較<br />\n但撤銷對所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n可以話係政府完全低頭認錯先會做<br />\n<br />\n而獨立調查委員會佢可以扮中立<br />\n話兩邊都有錯 兩邊都查<br />\n查幾多 幾多人會被檢控<br />\n真係好難講<br />\n<br />\nbtw 黨鐵出軌呢單野一定要煲大佢<br />\n起馬要整個獨立調查委員會<br />\n查佢老母利益輸送 偷工減料"},{"pid":"045c1588f88da17518effba91bf3331f3ce31458","tid":1575780,"uid":65790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:22:31.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"4db80520014c23d25dca207d4c4b78e825589cf7","tid":1575780,"uid":263150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:22:58.000Z","msg":"你賤到呢⋯"},{"pid":"854371a3098332a55bac349f52dfe58cdf87a5f9","tid":1575780,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32f291cf772db08faa7224c7013481cfc90e2446","tid":1575780,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:25:22.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"e8846a8344042c205d177643d9206297ad3e0c8a","tid":1575780,"uid":190239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:26:17.000Z","msg":"獨立調查-&gt;查完取消暴動定性 -&gt;所有義士無罪<br />\n<br />\n最後真普選"},{"pid":"0665fe06b0c0ef55d4ac10038481e00eeff8679c","tid":1575780,"uid":169195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:27:11.000Z","msg":"5大 全部都重要"},{"pid":"e4a2d07039ef1a6921540cd021b9e128d077648e","tid":1575780,"uid":70264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:28:39.000Z","msg":"有無嗌過缺一不可？<br